To Search with number named start, number named end, number named value, number named searchCalls
    Make number named current
    Set current to start + (end - start)/2
    Print with current
    If current == value
        Print with "Number of recursive calls: "
        Print with searchCalls
    Else
        If current < value
            Search with current, end, value, searchCalls + 1
        Else
            Search with start, current, value, searchCalls + 1

To Run
    Print with "Looking for 10 between 0-25"
    Search with 0, 25, 10, 1